## fping  (affects modules: netaddr, dns, icmp, seqmap)

The `netaddr` module's address-selection logic, the `icmp` module (echo
codec, ICMP sockets and the paced ping engine), the `seqmap` module
(sequence-number correlation map, after fping's seqmap.c), and the `dns`
module's /etc/hosts + UDP-PTR core DERIVE FROM fping
(https://github.com/schweikert/fping), a third-party work under the Stanford
license reproduced below. fping's license therefore applies to the derived
