## IANA Time Zone Database  (affects module: tz)

The `tz` module's zone table (`modules/tz/src/tz_data.zig`) is generated from
the IANA Time Zone Database (tzdata 2026a, https://www.iana.org/time-zones)
by the authors' `tz-gen` tool. The tz database is in the public domain, as
stated in its own distribution:

    This file is in the public domain, so clarified as of
    2009-05-17 by Arthur David Olson.

Only the UTC-offset transition data and POSIX-TZ footer rules are extracted
(not the tz database source code). The offset-lookup logic is the authors'
own (MIT).

