  blobmsg    — an original Zig implementation. The blob/blobmsg TLV codec
               (the bulk of the module) implements the OpenWRT libubox wire
               format from its headers blob.h/blobmsg.h (ISC) as the format
               specification — independent Zig implementation, no libubox code
